00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:49.000
Also in Joomla 4.2,
we have added keyboard shortcuts

00:27:49.000 --> 00:27:55.810
that will help people to move
faster through the Joomla site

00:27:55.810 --> 00:27:59.600
and make it easier to
make whatever they need.

00:28:01.260 --> 00:28:08.260
We are trying to make sure
that every new addition we put

00:28:08.260 --> 00:28:10.290
into Joomla is accessible.

00:28:13.970 --> 00:28:17.040
