00:31:32.680 --> 00:31:40.230
Seems until right now, we have
focused on making Joomla accessible

00:31:40.230 --> 00:31:43.020
for people who visit the website.

00:31:43.020 --> 00:31:47.770
We have also made it so
that Joomla can be used

00:31:47.770 --> 00:31:50.710
